{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my father was there, and my aunt-- my mother's sister-- was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they nursed me and mostly, you know, liquids, liquids, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when I got through, when the temperature went down, I think after-- it takes 14 days or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could not-- again, I could not walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I could not-- I, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- my legs were just like bone and skin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My arms, it just-- I was just like a skeleton after this because it happened a little bit before, during this hiding, and then [INAUDIBLE] you know, during this time that I was sick.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they started, you know, they started helping me, you know, to walk a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They held me under my arms until I could, you know, walk around a little bit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then I had very long hair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then [INAUDIBLE] they had to wash my hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then all my hair was out in this ball, you know, because after the sickness, you lose all your hair.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, and this was going on for about two or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I could hardly walk on my feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But then, one of-- [INAUDIBLE] in concentration-- I mean in the-- in ghetto came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they said, there's rumors that the ghetto is going to be surrounded, and they're going to finish off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So during the night I still-- I could hardly walk that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father and I-- this was, maybe, in February.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cold, and it was slick, ice, and snow, and mud, and all kind of-- so he dragged me by my arm, and we were walking and walking out from this, from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
